    "created_at": "2015-05-21T15:57:51Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-05-21T15:57:51Z",
    "body": "As of 10.10 there are APIs to, e.g., put the toolbar up in the title bar, use a transparent title bar, etc.\n\nSo it's certainly _possible_ to do these things. I suppose it's a question of whether Electron would want to expose those things, ideologically-speaking, and if so, what the API would look like.\n"
